Package org.universAAL.lddi.exporter.activityhub

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activator
    This bundle provides drivers for ActivityHub device services in OSGi registry.
    AHContextPublisher
    Provides context event patterns for the uAAL context bus
    AHManager
    Instantiates all ActivityHub drivers from ISO11073 library.
    AHServiceOntology
    Definition of service for the uAAL service bus (service profiles) for available ActivityHub devices.
    AHServiceProvider
    uAAL service provider (service bus) for the ActivityHub no ontology definitions here!
